You were going to leave without saying goodbye because you're embarrassed?

738
01:02:16.920 --> 01:02:22.660
Come out tomorrow. Let's eat lunch together and let us see you off.

739
01:02:22.660 --> 01:02:27.130
It's bothersome. You should go and take care of them. They're probably drunk.

740
01:02:27.130 --> 01:02:30.920
I don't want to. I want to take care of you.

741
01:02:32.360 --> 01:02:35.730
Being nice is also a disease. Don't try and take in everybody once you're the chief editor.

742
01:02:35.730 --> 01:02:37.260
You need to be mean when you need to.

743
01:02:37.260 --> 01:02:39.150
I don't even know if they'll give me that position.

744
01:02:39.150 --> 01:02:43.160
If they don't, tell me. I'll come with my baby.

745
01:02:43.160 --> 01:02:45.430
It seems you'll really come.

746
01:02:47.840 --> 01:02:50.000
Are you not going to follow?

747
01:02:53.750 --> 01:02:55.290
Let's go together.

748
01:02:55.290 --> 01:02:57.370
Hurry!

749
01:03:02.810 --> 01:03:04.620
Are you really just going to leave?

750
01:03:04.620 --> 01:03:08.190
At least say goodbye. Since it's the last.

751
01:03:08.190 --> 01:03:10.970
Shall I cry while hugging them tightly?

752
01:03:10.970 --> 01:03:13.510
Wouldn't it be embarrassing if I see them again?

753
01:03:13.510 --> 01:03:17.960
That's true. It'll be very embarrassing!

754
01:03:20.950 --> 01:03:23.800
- Chief editor. Chief editor!
 - Hey.

755
01:03:23.800 --> 01:03:26.090
