756
01:03:32.950 --> 01:03:35.730
I'm thankful for you.

757
01:03:38.630 --> 01:03:42.340
Very... much.

758
01:03:45.990 --> 01:03:47.820
Me too.

759
01:03:48.620 --> 01:03:50.700
Thank you.

760
01:03:52.630 --> 01:03:54.700
You called a driver?

761
01:03:54.700 --> 01:03:57.130
Yes.

762
01:03:57.130 --> 01:03:59.420
