764
01:04:51.810 --> 01:04:54.630
Oh, it's Hari!

765
01:04:56.580 --> 01:04:57.750
Let's go for round two.

766
01:04:57.750 --> 01:04:59.400
We have to go for round two!

767
01:04:59.400 --> 01:05:01.720
Ow!

768
01:05:01.720 --> 01:05:04.510
Go home! Hurry!

769
01:05:04.510 --> 01:05:05.710
This car is round two.

770
01:05:05.710 --> 01:05:07.260
You all head in first.

771
01:05:07.260 --> 01:05:09.550
I'll take care of everything,

772
01:05:09.550 --> 01:05:10.720
so go for the second round.

773
01:05:10.720 --> 01:05:13.820
