- Stay here. 
 - General Manager!

781
01:05:30.330 --> 01:05:32.660
Get in.

782
01:05:32.660 --> 01:05:35.790
Eutteum! Get a hold of yourself.

783
01:05:35.790 --> 01:05:39.050
