784
01:05:39.050 --> 01:05:41.060
Mr. Eutteum, snap out of it. Are you okay?

785
01:05:41.060 --> 01:05:43.140
I'll take care of things on this end.

786
01:05:43.140 --> 01:05:44.640
You go and help them inside.

787
01:05:44.640 --> 01:05:46.790
I'll help over here so you can go there.

788
01:05:46.790 --> 01:05:49.490
Chief, help us here.

789
01:05:49.490 --> 01:05:53.390
I have something to say to Deputy Editor.

790
01:05:53.390 --> 01:05:54.630
I'll-I'll figure something out.

791
01:05:54.630 --> 01:05:55.820
Just get in.

792
01:05:55.820 --> 01:05:59.610
I... have something to confess...

793
01:05:59.610 --> 01:06:03.020
Mr. Eutteum, you know who I am, right?

794
01:06:03.020 --> 01:06:05.160
- You're my aunt. 
 - What?

795
01:06:07.630 --> 01:06:09.020
Deputy Editor!

796
01:06:09.020 --> 01:06:12.110
Get a hold of yourself.

797
01:06:12.110 --> 01:06:13.570
All right!

798
01:06:13.570 --> 01:06:16.030
I shouldn't get in this car.

799
01:06:16.030 --> 01:06:20.530
Excuse me, I called a taxi, so we're gonna go wait over there. You take care of them there.

800
01:06:20.530 --> 01:06:22.770
Okay, okay.

801
01:06:22.770 --> 01:06:26.600
- My car, my car. 
 - It's this one.

802
01:06:26.600 --> 01:06:29.280
But this isn't my car! My car is a—

803
01:06:29.280 --> 01:06:30.400
