817
01:07:35.930 --> 01:07:39.830
Are you trying to look good in front of me?

818
01:07:42.390 --> 01:07:44.200
What?

819
01:07:50.320 --> 01:07:54.120
I also... want to look good in front of you.

820
01:07:55.350 --> 01:07:57.140
Ah, seriously.

